snippet.title: Jack Sparrow Testifies Against Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Jack Sparrow Testifies Against Amber Heard

By bringing up his past relationship with Kate Moss (and a fictitious incident) she has now opened the door to not only Kate testifying- now his lawyers are allowed to bring up all past relationships- including her previous DV arrest.
